### Prerequisites for Full Functionality

To fully enable Vercel Web Analytics:
1. Project must be deployed to Vercel
2. Analytics must be enabled in the Vercel dashboard (Analytics tab → Enable)
3. After deployment, the app will start sending analytics data automatically
4. Data will begin appearing in the Vercel dashboard after initial traffic

### Next Steps

After deployment to Vercel:
1. Visit the Vercel dashboard and enable Web Analytics (if not already enabled)
2. Monitor the Analytics tab for visitor data, page views, and other metrics
3. Use the filtering tools to analyze performance and user behavior
4. For advanced tracking, custom events can be added using the `track()` function from `@vercel/analytics/react`
